# Scoring Rules

## Score Calculation
- Base = 100, subtract per finding using SEVERITY_DEDUCTIONS
- Multiply by field-specific multiplier if check_id prefix matches
- Add bonuses for good practices (absence of common findings)
- Clamp final to [0, 100]

## Grade Thresholds
A+ ≥ 90 (brightgreen), A ≥ 80 (green), B ≥ 70 (yellowgreen),
C ≥ 60 (yellow), D ≥ 45 (orange), F < 45 (red)

## Badge
- shields.io URL with for-the-badge style
- Markdown and HTML embeds available
- score_summary_markdown() generates full report with table
